    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver or a great project for someone looking to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics and climate controls remain functional. It has been regularly serviced, but prospective buyers should expect the typical mechanical wear associated with a car of this age and mileage. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 20000.0,
